&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-GB"&gt;As
mentioned this accident is still under police investigation, and&amp;nbsp;the
company will be prosecuted according to Norwegian legislation. This report will
be updated as the results from the legal process are known.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

